Task: Fix the CI/CD issue by updating the .github/workflows/ci-test.yml file to replace Hugo with Vitepress.

The file currently has these Hugo-related steps in the \"test\" job:
1. A \"Setup Hugo\" step using peaceiris/actions-hugo@v2
2. A \"Cache Hugo resources\" step
3. A \"Build Docs\" step that uses Hugo

Remove steps 1 and 2 completely, and modify step 3 to use Vitepress instead of Hugo.

The current \"Build Docs\" step looks like:
```yaml
- name: Build Docs
  run: |
    cp .env.example .env
    cd docs/site && hugo && cd ../..
```

Change it to:
```yaml
- name: Build Docs
  run: |
    cp .env.example .env
    cd docs/site && npm install && NODE_ENV=production npm run docs:build && cd ../..
```

Keep all other parts of the file unchanged.
